	        Reef Snorkeling: Explore vibrant coral reefs teeming with colorful marine life. This activity is perfect for snorkelers of all skill levels and offers the chance to encounter an array of tropical fish, sea turtles, and other fascinating creatures.
	    </p>
	</div>
	
	<div>
