	        Cave Snorkeling: Venture into underwater caves and caverns for an exciting snorkeling adventure. Discover hidden chambers, intricate rock formations, and the mysterious creatures that inhabit these secluded underwater environments.
	    </p>
	</div>
	
	<div>
	    <img src="pictures/snorkeling-safari.jpg" alt="Boat Picture">
	    <p>
	        Snorkeling Safari: Embark on guided snorkeling expeditions to remote and pristine locations. Snorkeling safaris offer the opportunity to explore diverse marine ecosystems, from secluded lagoons and mangrove forests to open ocean habitats, under the guidance of experienced naturalists.
	    </p>
	</div>

